attributes.action: Reduce foreign aid in favour of increasing pensions with immediate effect
attributes.background: We pay far too much to third world countries some of which have a space exploration programme when our pensioners are the one if the lowest pay in Europe. I find this unacceptable reading how some freeze to death because of such low pension payments. We are the laughing stock of the world.
